<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-89-0668 </DOCNO><TEXT>Electric power system long range operation planning with the emphasison the coal inventory is treated for the period ranging from one monthto one year. A mathematical model of coal inventory planning is giventaking into account seasonal hydro storage plants operation, contractedand other imports and exports of electric energy and projected load diagrams.A method is given which solves the problem of optimal fuel managementpolicy along with the practical example of electric power system plannedoperation.</TEXT></DOC>